        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 3. Solariella illustris Sturany, 1900, Station 48 (Yanbu' al Bahr, Saudi Arabia, Red Sea). A-D, F-G. Figured syntype, NHMW 84287: front (A), right side (B), back (C), top (D), bottom (F), apex (G). E. Original figure by Sturany (1903). Scale bars: A-D, F: 2 mm, G: 0.2 mm." ;
